<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3825763>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Gergithus frontilongus sp. nov. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Metope and clypeus, facial view. D. Metope and clypeus, lateral view. E. Fore leg, mid leg, hind leg. F. Tegmen. G. Hind wing. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3825763/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3825769>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Gergithus spp. A–C. Gergithus sp. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, frontal view. C. Habitus, lateral view. — D–F. Gergithus cribratus Melichar, 1906. D. Habitus, dorsal view. E. Habitus, lateral view. F. Frons and clypeus, facial view. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3825769/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3825771>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Gergithus signatifrons Melichar, 1906, syntype. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Metope and clypeus, frontolateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Metope and clypeus, facial view. E. Habitus, lateral view. F. Labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3825771/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3825773>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Hemisphaerini. A–D. Gergithus schaumi (Stål, 1855), syntype. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Metope and clypeus, facial view. D. Label. — E–F. Gergithus frontilongus sp. nov. E. Metope and clypeus, lateral view. F. Metope and clypeus, facial view. — G–H. Gnezdilovius iguchii (Matsumura, 1916) comb. nov. G. Metope and clypeus, lateral view. H. Metope and clypeus, facial view. Arrows points the anteclypeus angular or compressed." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3825773/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

